title: Sidewall, 1976-48-43, 1860–80
inscribed: Inscribed on recto in graphite: "squares/ go up and down", "change flowers" and "...width 20 1/2". There are also small brushstrokes of red and pink near center of paper on recto.
description: Diamond diaper pattern. Mauve and green outline framework with small squares at junctions. Two different floral sprigs alternate within framework. Printed on ungrounded paper.
